restSimpleBinding.body: <soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"> <soap:Header/> <soap:Body> <ns:getProcessListInput xmlns:ns="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/activebpeladmin/2007/01/activebpeladmin.xsd"> { if(boolean($getProcessList/filter)) then <ns:filter> <ns1:listStart xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd">{$getProcessList/filter/listStart/text()}</ns1:listStart> <ns1:maxReturn xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd">{$getProcessList/filter/maxReturn/text()}</ns1:maxReturn> { for $processState in $getProcessList/filter/processState return <ns:processState>{$processState/text()}</ns:processState> } <ns:processName namespace="{$getProcessList/filter/processName/namespace/text()}">{$getProcessList/filter/processName/text()}</ns:processName> <ns:created> <ns1:on xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd">{$getProcessList/filter/created/on/text()}</ns1:on> <ns1:between xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd" fromDate="{$getProcessList/filter/created/between/fromDate/text()}" optional="true" toDate="{$getProcessList/filter/created/between/toDate/text()}"/> </ns:created> <ns:completed> <ns1:on xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd">{$getProcessList/filter/completed/on/text()}</ns1:on> <ns1:between xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd" fromDate="{$getProcessList/filter/completed/between/fromDate/text()}" optional="true" toDate="{$getProcessList/filter/completed/between/toDate/text()}"/> </ns:completed> <ns:processGroup>{$getProcessList/filter/processGroup/text()}</ns:processGroup> <ns:hideSystem>{$getProcessList/filter/hideSystem/text()}</ns:hideSystem> <ns:advancedQuery>{$getProcessList/filter/advancedQuery/text()}</ns:advancedQuery> <ns:hidePublicTenant>{$getProcessList/filter/hidePublicTenant/text()}</ns:hidePublicTenant> </ns:filter> else if(boolean($getProcessList/processIdFilter)) then <ns:processIdFilter> { for $processId in $getProcessList/processIdFilter/processId return <ns:processId>{$processId/text()}</ns:processId> } </ns:processIdFilter> else () } </ns:getProcessListInput> </soap:Body> </soap:Envelope>
